data.description:
Rare opportunity to own a stunning home in Washington County's most coveted neighborhood. Embrace the charm of small-town living while enjoying the breathtaking trails of the Santa Clara River Reserve right at your doorstep. This high-end premium custom built home has a spacious & inviting main floor, a chef's kitchen with large walk-in pantry, butler fridge, dual ovens, artisan cabinetry & tasteful appliances, an exceptional home office, sizeable bedrooms, a large laundry room, a dedicated theater, a cozy library & the ultimate game room for entertaining. Step outside to an idyllic outdoor living space with a covered patio that extends under a beautifully ornate pergola surrounded by resort-level landscaping, framing a unique & alluring pool & hot tub perfect for relaxation & hosting Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this home features 2x6 framing throughout, top-end hardwood floors, exposed beams, & first-rate woodwork & stonework. No expense was spared in its construction. Building a new home to this level of construction would cost above $400 per square foot, not including lot price and landscaping. The massive garage offers plenty of storage, & the substantial RV garage, easily capable of storing a boat or motorhome, is currently dialed in as a climate-controlled, multi-functional athletic space adjacent to an inventive, complete home gym.  Additionally, there is a considerable exterior RV pad capable of even more creative uses. 

Welcome your guests to a spacious, private, detached casita with den, kitchenette & full bathroom. Golf enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to 5 golf courses within 8 minutes, including a premier country club & a destination resort (10 courses within 18 minutes). Outdoor enthusiasts can explore nearby Snow Canyon and a myriad of other trails and parks, while arts & culture lovers can enjoy the Tuacahn Amphitheater & Kayenta Arts Center.

This community is known for its safety, excellent schools, & residents who value decency & patriotism. Don't miss your chance to make this extraordinary property your forever home.
